content: This living room is ample in size, with a minimalist design aesthetic. The color palette primarily consists of shades of white, gray, and black. The room has large windows that let in natural light, tall ceiling, and a simple white window treatment. The furniture is minimal, composed of natural materials such as wood, leather and wool, with clean lines and simple geometric design. The decor is kept to a minimal, with a few select pieces of Icelandic art or handmade crafts on display. Lighting fixtures are also minimalistic and clean-lined. The overall design of the space is uncluttered and sleek, reflecting the minimalistic Icelandic style.
